task.summary: Changed near everything Big refactoring. Now the program is more suitable under the terms of project. Much more like MVC, but some troubles still exist. I could not figure out how to implement past ideas.
Added prices to sellable items, first steps to implement vendors.
Added vendor to the square, "Trade" button for gui, needed some improvements
Created new "Trading Screen" form, added some DataGridView's. About 2.5 hours from working vendors
Created Vendor!!! Noticed some bug with "Attack" button when changed "SelectedWeapon" and bug when trying to start "Trade" outside of Square.
That's what I call BIG DICK REFACTORING
